---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Features — SessionFS" activeNav="features" description="SessionFS features: capture, resume, audit, handoff, sync, and more.">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-5 relative noise">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6" style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans';">Everything you need</h1>
        <p class="text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Capture sessions from 8 tools. Resume anywhere. Audit for hallucinations. Share with teammates.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <a href="/features/judge/" class="glass p-6 block">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="text-3xl shrink-0">&#9878;</div><div><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">LLM Judge</h3><p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Cross-references every AI claim against actual tool outputs. Severity-classified findings.</p><div class="text-sm px-3 py-1.5 rounded" style="background: rgba(10,12,16,0.5); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; color: #3ddc84;">CRITICAL — "Test passes" but exit code 1</div></div></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/features/handoff/" class="glass p-6 block">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="text-3xl shrink-0">&#128101;</div><div><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Team Handoff</h3><p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Hand off sessions to teammates with full context. Session data copies to recipient.</p><div class="text-sm px-3 py-1.5 rounded" style="background: rgba(10,12,16,0.5); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; color: #3ddc84;">sfs handoff ses_abc --to sarah@co.dev</div></div></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/features/summary/" class="glass p-6 block">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="text-3xl shrink-0">&#128203;</div><div><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Session Summary</h3><p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #c9d1d9;">See what happened in 10 seconds. Files, tests, commands extracted automatically.</p><div class="text-sm px-3 py-1.5 rounded" style="background: rgba(10,12,16,0.5); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; color: #3ddc84;">3 modified &middot; 5/6 tests &middot; 34 commands</div></div></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/features/mcp/" class="glass p-6 block">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="text-3xl shrink-0">&#9881;</div><div><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">MCP Server</h3><p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #c9d1d9;">AI agents search your past sessions and read project context. 5 tools via MCP.</p><div class="text-sm px-3 py-1.5 rounded" style="background: rgba(10,12,16,0.5); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; color: #3ddc84;">sfs mcp install --for claude-code</div></div></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/autosync/" class="glass p-6 block">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="text-3xl shrink-0">&#9729;</div><div><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Cloud Sync &amp; Autosync</h3><p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Push to the cloud, pull on any machine. Three modes: off, all, selective.</p><div class="text-sm px-3 py-1.5 rounded" style="background: rgba(10,12,16,0.5); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; color: #3ddc84;">sfs sync auto --mode all</div></div></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/git-integration/" class="glass p-6 block">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="text-3xl shrink-0">&#128279;</div><div><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">GitHub &amp; GitLab</h3><p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #c9d1d9;">AI session context on every PR and MR. Contradictions surfaced for reviewers.</p><div class="text-sm px-3 py-1.5 rounded" style="background: rgba(10,12,16,0.5); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; color: #3ddc84;">Cloud + self-hosted GitLab</div></div></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/cli/" class="glass p-6 block">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="text-3xl shrink-0">&#128269;</div><div><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Full-Text Search</h3><p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Search across all sessions by keyword, error message, or file path.</p><div class="text-sm px-3 py-1.5 rounded" style="background: rgba(10,12,16,0.5); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; color: #3ddc84;">sfs search "rate limiting"</div></div></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/sfs-format/" class="glass p-6 block">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="text-3xl shrink-0">&#128194;</div><div><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Workspace Aware</h3><p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Git state captured automatically — branch, commit, remote URL, dirty files.</p><div class="text-sm px-3 py-1.5 rounded" style="background: rgba(10,12,16,0.5); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; color: #3ddc84;">feature/auth-fix @ a1b2c3d</div></div></div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
